<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaiun, Nang haw, lo a buh atte,
 Hat lo leh thingilh in;
 Lalpa deihum chuh ngakzing hitiu,
 Ei hih hat thak ina.

[V2]
 &quot;Lalpa a na ngak zingte chuh,
 Hatna thak nei in, Tha-in lengto untin;
 Mu bangin tha in lengto untin,
 Tai un tin, mahleh chawl puonau,
 Thingilh lo a chieh ding;
 Tai un tin, mahleh chawl puonau,
 Chaulo a chieh ding.&quot;

[V3]
 2. Tamtak vei chuh gim le lungkham in,
 A chunga I phunchiek;
 Hukdampa hing chuh gingcha zingin,
 Bangdin I thingilh dem?

[V4]
 3. Kipak un! I kawmah A um zing,
 Khawvel tawp chan inle;
 Dak un, hang takin masuon zel un,
 I thilkhawk ei piena!</lyrics>
<title>THEY THAT WAIT UPON THE LORD'</title>
</song>